WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.800
You arrive at your desk to find an unmarked envelope containing a USB drive.

00:06.000 --> 00:11.000
It holds audio recordings proving a high-ranking executive is accepting bribes.

00:11.500 --> 00:15.800
A note reads: 'I'm too scared to report this. Please help.'

00:16.000 --> 00:18.000
How do you handle this evidence?